	)
	(text_box "This is a carrier board for a Raspberry Pi Compute Module 5.\n\nIt features the standard CM5 IO of USB, Ethernet and MIPI, as well as an M.2 E-key slot and a 1000BASE-T1 single pair Ethernet PHY.\n\nIn order to have a second Ethernet port and an M.2 slot the single PCIe gen2/3 lane connects to a PCI11010C switch which includes an Ethernet MAC.\n\nThe power tree is designed to be robust and handle the worst case consumption of all peripherals."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
